ous point of pride that I was able to persevere down there toward the lair and complete the Kunark book.</P><P>Part of me wants to see it changed to even it all out, but the other part doesn't want to take away the chance at feeling the serious pride of completing the whole set from other people.  As unbalanced as it might seem - If you fight there, you'll get 'em.</P><P>(I don't believe that it's *intentional* that it distributes the way that it does, but rather a weakness in the way our system handles loot tables with an extremely large list of items to pick from.)</P><P><BR>Therefore, if you take nothing else from this, let it be that this message proves is that I am wholly incapable of making a long story anything but...well.. long. :)</P><P>Best,</P><P>- Scott<BR></font></td>
